{"tid":1667233,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢諗到快除背囊方法","createTime":"2019-10-21T10:48:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T10:57:18.000Z","uid":5220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6a95bbefc6a3dfbae728d5eb0fb4a600c2c6f260","tid":1667233,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:48:16.000Z","msg":"狗好鍾意咬背囊<br />\n好多手足衰係呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人話要買快拆背囊，又要all black嘅話選擇又少<br />\n<br />\n有日發夢忽然諗到個方法俾有胸帶嘅普通背囊用：<br />\n<br />\n肩帶放到好長，好似以前d MK仔咁放到個袋磨屎忽嘅，前臂要好容易穿返入肩帶個圈除袋<br />\n如果你膊頭唔夠橫，個袋應該係成日想瀡落黎咁<br />\n<br />\n然後扣胸帶防止個袋真係跌<br />\n萬一俾狗咬袋，一啪開胸帶個扣就可以甩身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02fd858b3573b15afdf80f4d134f958a07e7d651","tid":1667233,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:54:39.000Z","msg":"個袋咁樣應該跑唔郁"},{"pid":"e010b6b08fda4b4ca808db0f6e7647b03d05a0d7","tid":1667233,"uid":181502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:55:30.000Z","msg":"點跑呀大佬，你估我未試過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9145caa63fa063c52011e04b2d94578554dd2e6e","tid":1667233,"uid":294835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:57:18.000Z","msg":"孭單邊咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}